OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FFrance has become the first European
OL,7,Fcountry to ban social media for
OL,8,Fchildren after Australia sparked a
OL,9,Fwave of legislative interest in the
OL,10,Fmove last year.
OL,12,FAustralia implemented restrictions on
OL,13,FTikTok, Instagram, Facebook, X,
OL,14,FSnapchat, YouTube, Kick, Twitch,
OL,15,FThreads, and Reddit in December.
OL,17,FThe rule change caused huge
OL,18,Fcontroversy, with strong voices both
OL,19,Ffor and against the law. But now,
OL,20,Fother countries are following suit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
