OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FIn July, lawmakers approved a bill
OL,7,Fbanning social media for children
OL,8,Funder 15.
OL,10,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron has
OL,11,Fasked for the legislation to be fast-
OL,12,Ftracked, so that it could be in place
OL,13,Fby the start of the next school year
OL,14,Fin September.
OL,16,F"France is leading the way in Europe
OL,17,Fin protecting our children and our
OL,18,Fteenagers," Macron said. "We will keep
OL,19,Fon going."
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@KO]zD@ZOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/24
