OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FIt would also ban the use of mobile
OL,7,Fphones in high schools.
OL,9,FAccording to France's health watchdog,
OL,10,Fone in two teenagers spends between
OL,11,Ftwo and five hours a day on a
OL,12,Fsmartphone.
OL,14,FDenmark announced in October that it
OL,15,Fwould be moving towards banning social
OL,16,Fmedia for users under 15.
OL,18,FPrime Minister Mette Frederiksen said
OL,19,Fat the time that social platforms were
OL,20,F"stealing our children's childhood".
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/24
