OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FSpeaking at the opening of the Danish
OL,7,Fparliament, Frederiksen said her
OL,8,Fgovernment would propose a ban that
OL,9,Falso gives parents the option to
OL,10,Fapprove social media use from age 13.
OL,12,F"We have said yes to mobile phones in
OL,13,Four children's lives in the best
OL,14,Fsense. So they can call home and
OL,15,Fcommunicate with their friends," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/24
