OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"But the reality is that we have let a
OL,7,Fmonster loose. Never before have so
OL,8,Fmany children and young people
OL,9,Fsuffered from anxiety and depression,"
OL,10,FFrederiksen added.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FCanada has introduced legislation that
OL,18,Fcould bar children younger than 16
OL,19,Ffrom having social media accounts
OL,20,Funless the companies show they can
OL,21,Fmake their platforms safe.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]
