OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"We are failing our children. Enough
OL,7,Fis enough," Marc Miller, Canada's
OL,8,Fculture minister, said. "We need basic
OL,9,Fprotection in place."
OL,11,FThe legislation covers seven types of
OL,12,Fharmful content including content that
OL,13,Finduces children to harm themselves,
OL,14,Fcontent that incites violence and
OL,15,Ffoments hatred and non-consensual
OL,16,Fintimate images.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@KO]pD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/24
