OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FA new regulator, the Digital Safety
OL,7,FCommission of Canada, will be created
OL,8,Fas part of the plans. Miller said
OL,9,Fplatforms will need to prove they are
OL,10,Fsafe and age verification measures
OL,11,Fwill also be introduced.
OL,13,FNorway's Prime Minister Jonas Gahr
OL,14,FStore has also proposed a ban for
OL,15,Fusers under 15 years of age and his
OL,16,Fgovernment launched a public
OL,17,Fconsultation for a new law in June.
OL,26,@vD@Co|
