OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"This is one of the most pressing
OL,7,Fsocial and cultural challenges of our
OL,8,Ftime, and it cannot be solved through
OL,9,Fnational measures alone. We aim to
OL,10,Fstrengthen European cooperation to
OL,11,Fensure a safe digital environment for
OL,12,Fchildren and young people," Store said
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FAlongside the ban, Norway has said it
OL,16,Fwould issue national recommendations
OL,17,Fon screen times and remove mobile
OL,18,Fphones from schools through national
OL,19,Frecommendations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@[O]tD@_o|
