OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FUK ministers launched a consultation
OL,7,Fon whether to ban under-16s from
OL,8,Fsocial media platforms earlier this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FOvernight curfews, breaks to prevent
OL,12,F"doom-scrolling", and introducing an
OL,13,FAustralian-style social media ban
OL,14,Fwhich would raise the digital age of
OL,15,Fconsent, are some of the proposals the
OL,16,Fgovernment is considering.
OL,18,FITV News understands at least 66
OL,19,FLabour MPs want the government to
OL,20,Fbring in a social media ban for under-
OL,21,F16s.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/24
