OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FThey raised concerns around teenagers'
OL,7,Frising mental health issues, their
OL,8,Finability to focus on learning, and
OL,9,Fthat they are "not building the social
OL,10,Fskills needed to thrive", adding that
OL,11,Fthe average 12-year-old spends 29
OL,12,Fhours per week on a smartphone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
