OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FWhile the government is so far yet to
OL,7,Fintroduce a ban, in June, former Prime
OL,8,FMinister Kier Starmer announced that
OL,9,Fbig tech companies including Google
OL,10,Fand Apple must introduce controls to
OL,11,F"prevent children from sending and
OL,12,Freceiving sexually explicit images" `
OL,13,Fgiving them three months to comply
OL,14,Fwith the law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/24
