OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FIn March Indonesia became the first
OL,7,Fcountry in Southeast Asia to ban
OL,8,Fchildren from having accounts on
OL,9,FYouTube, TikTok, Facebook, Instagram,
OL,10,FThreads, X, Bigo Live and Roblox with
OL,11,Fnew legislation.
OL,13,FThe legislation bans children under 16
OL,14,Ffrom accessing digital platforms that
OL,15,Fcould expose them to pornography,
OL,16,Fcyberbullying, online scams and
OL,17,Faddiction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/24
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
