OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FBut Meta Managing Director William
OL,7,FEaston made it clear that the method
OL,8,Fwould not be the company's preferred
OL,9,Fway of protecting young people.
OL,11,F"We're committed to meeting our
OL,12,Fcompliance obligations and are taking
OL,13,Fthe necessary steps to comply with the
OL,14,Flaw. That said, we hope to continue
OL,15,Fengaging constructively with the
OL,16,FAustralian government to find a better
OL,17,Fway forward," he said.
