OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FSnapchat and TikTok similarly
OL,7,Fdeactivated accounts of people under
OL,8,F16 and placed age restrictions on
OL,9,Fcreating new accounts.
OL,11,FReddit launched a legal challenge
OL,12,Fagainst Australia's ban, saying that
OL,13,Fit isolates teens "from the ability to
OL,14,Fengage in age-appropriate community
OL,15,Fexperiences".
OL,17,FThe platform complied with the ban but
OL,18,Fchallenged the law over concerns about
OL,19,Fprivacy and political rights, and
OL,20,Fargued that the new law fails to
OL,21,Fprotect children online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/24
